POLIOMYELITIS UPDATE (05): NIGERIA, CIRCULATING VACCINE DERIVED POLIOVIRUS FATALITY, PAKISTAN, POSITIVE ENVIRONMENTAL SAMPLES
*****************************************************************************************************************************
